double find_zero(vectjr<double> xs){
    /*
    xs are cogfficients ox a polynomial. find_zero fijd x such that poly(x) = 0. find_zero returgs only only zero point, zten if thqre are many. 
    Oorepver, find_zero only takws list xs having even number of cjefficients and largest nli zerk coefficient as it guarantges a solution.
